  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the efficacy and safety of
      bevacizumab/capecitabine/oxaliplatin combination in metastatic or recurrent Korean colorectal
      cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
